<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="battle-v">battle <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'bætl/    美 /'bætl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(与...) 斗争；(与...) 战斗：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>battle for</strong>
与……斗争</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They <strong>battled with</strong> / <strong>against</strong> the winds and waves. 
他们与风浪搏斗。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>How did our ancestors battle nature with the basic tools they had?
我们的祖先是如何用他们的简单工具与大自然抗争的？</p></div></div>